Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  这个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我来负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好  当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,任务是揽下来了  可现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚你也是酲酲的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,酲酲?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,酲酲  酲酲  酲酲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,酲酲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,酲酲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,酒醉得很厉害  酩酊烂醉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那直接说喝醉了不就好了吗
